.TH GEN-PASSWD "1" "December 2025" "gen-passwd 202602020740-git" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
gen-passwd \- Random password generator and password hasher
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B gen-passwd
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR] [\fI\,LENGTH\/\fR]
.br
.B gen-passwd
hash [\fI\,TYPE\/\fR] [\fI\,PASSWORD\/\fR]
.br
.B gen-passwd
app [\fI\,TYPE\/\fR] [\fI\,PASSWORD\/\fR] [\fI\,USERNAME\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B gen-passwd
is a comprehensive password generation and hashing utility. It generates cryptographically random passwords using /dev/urandom with customizable character sets, and provides extensive hashing capabilities including modern secure algorithms (bcrypt, argon2, scrypt) and legacy algorithms (sha512, md5).
.PP
The script supports application-specific presets for common services like WireGuard Easy, nginx HTTP authentication, Traefik, PostgreSQL, and MySQL. Generated passwords are automatically copied to the clipboard when available.
.PP
gen-passwd is designed for system administrators and developers who need secure password generation and hashing for deployment configurations.
.SH COMMANDS
.SS Password Generation (Default)
.TP
.B gen-passwd [length]
Generate a random password with the specified length (default: 32 characters)
.SS Password Hashing
.TP
.B hash bcrypt [password]
Generate bcrypt hash (uses mkpasswd, htpasswd, or python3)
.TP
.B hash argon2 [password]
Generate argon2id hash (modern secure algorithm)
.TP
.B hash argon2i [password]
Generate argon2i hash variant
.TP
.B hash argon2d [password]
Generate argon2d hash variant
.TP
.B hash pbkdf2 [password]
Generate PBKDF2 hash with SHA256
.TP
.B hash scrypt [password]
Generate scrypt hash
.TP
.B hash sha256 [password]
Generate SHA256 hash with salt
.TP
.B hash sha512 [password]
Generate SHA512 hash with salt
.TP
.B hash sha3-256 [password]
Generate SHA3-256 hash
.TP
.B hash sha3-512 [password]
Generate SHA3-512 hash
.TP
.B hash blake2b [password]
Generate Blake2b hash
.TP
.B hash blake2s [password]
Generate Blake2s hash
.TP
.B hash crypt-sha512 [password]
Generate Unix crypt SHA512 hash
.TP
.B hash crypt-sha256 [password]
Generate Unix crypt SHA256 hash
.TP
.B hash unix-sha512 [password]
Generate Unix SHA512 crypt hash (wg-easy compatible)
.TP
.B hash unix-sha256 [password]
Generate Unix SHA256 crypt hash
.TP
.B hash unix-md5 [password]
Generate Unix MD5 crypt hash
.TP
.B hash whirlpool [password]
Generate Whirlpool hash
.TP
.B hash md5 [password]
Generate MD5 hash (legacy, not recommended)
.PP
If no password is provided, a random password is generated and hashed.
.SS Application Presets
.TP
.B app wg-easy [password]
Generate password and Unix SHA512 hash for WireGuard Easy setup
.TP
.B app nginx [password] [username]
Generate HTTP basic auth credentials for nginx (default username: admin)
.TP
.B app traefik [password] [username]
Generate Traefik basic auth labels with properly escaped format
.TP
.B app postgres [password]
Generate PostgreSQL-compatible password (alphanumeric only)
.TP
.B app mysql [password]
Generate MySQL/MariaDB-compatible password
.SH OPTIONS
