Set the working directory (primarily for configuration purposes)
.SS Password Generation Options
.TP
.BR \-\-length " " \fI\,N\/\fR
Set the password length (default: 32)
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-numbers
Exclude numbers (0-9) from password
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-chars
Exclude special characters (@ _ -) from password
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-upper
Exclude uppercase letters (A-Z) from password
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-lower
Exclude lowercase letters (a-z) from password
.SS Hash Output Options
.TP
.BR \-\-docker
Format output for Docker compose files (escapes $ as $$)
.TP
.BR \-\-prefix
Include algorithm prefix in the hash output
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B gen-passwd
Generate a 32-character random password
.TP
.B gen-passwd 16
Generate a 16-character password
.TP
.B gen-passwd --no-chars 24
Generate 24-character password without special characters
.TP
.B gen-passwd hash bcrypt
Generate random password and create bcrypt hash
.TP
.B gen-passwd hash unix-sha512 mypassword
Create Unix SHA512 hash of "mypassword"
.TP
.B gen-passwd --docker hash unix-sha512
Generate hash formatted for docker-compose.yml
.TP
.B gen-passwd app wg-easy
Generate WireGuard Easy setup with password and hash
.TP
.B gen-passwd app nginx mypass admin
Create nginx auth for user "admin" with password "mypass"
.TP
.B gen-passwd app traefik
Generate Traefik basic auth labels with random password
